}{\plain \fs24 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b 85.}{\plain \fs24   See the note to }{\plain \fs24 \i Inferno}{\plain \fs24  V.61-62.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b 86. }{\plain \fs24  On the Virgilian context and possible consequent effect of Dante's word }{\plain \fs24 \i maligno}{\plain \fs24 , see \softline
