follows: it reads either (1) }{\plain \fs24 \i si tace}{\plain \fs24  (becomes silent); or (2a) }{\plain \fs24 \i ci tace}{\plain \fs24  (grows quiet here); or (2b) }{\plain \fs24 \i ci \softline
tace}{\plain \fs24  (grows quiet for our sake).  Petrocchi (}{\plain \fs24 \i La Commedia secondo l'antica vulgata}{\plain \fs24 , }{\plain \fs24 \i Inferno}{\plain \fs24 ), pp. \softline
