force of Paolo's love still wounds, or afflicts, or dominates me]).\par
}{\plain \fs24 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b 103.}{\plain \fs24   The }{\plain \fs24 \i dicta}{\plain \fs24  of Andreas Capellanus are often cited as lying behind Francesca's speech \softline
